lead_paragraph: Tina Thompson scored 23 points last night to lead the Comets to a 97-62 victory over the Liberty in Houston. Despite playing without Sheryl Swoopes, Houston never trailed. Iciss Tillis led the Liberty with 12 points before fouling out.
